For ALL coding tasks, follow the development standards in C:\Users\Kratos\.config\ai-rules\rules.md

Key rules (MUST follow):
- 2 spaces indentation (never tabs)
- camelCase (local variables), PascalCase (global variables), UPPER_SNAKE_CASE (constants)
- Commits: "Type: Description" format (Add, Fix, Update, Remove, Refactor, Docs)
- Explicit error handling, never silent failures
- Never commit secrets, use .env files
- Line wrap at 80, max 100 characters
- Files: kebab-case naming
- Comments: explain "why", not "what"

